---
title: West African Chicken and Peanut Stew with scallion and bulgur wheat
description: Often called ground nut stew, peanut stew is a staple in West African cuisine that has many variations. This recipe is a chicken version and is also filled with delicious grains and vibrant veg.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W28_IE_IECC25673-2_Main__2high-4407bec0.jpg
